ProductDescription:
Details 

Multipack fit comfortable boxers briefs made from cotton and Spandex.

* Classic fit comfort briefs

* Made from 95% cotton and 5% spandex

* Kerryco. logo on the waistband with KC logo on front corner of the boxers

* Machine wash cold, tunmble dry with low heat and cool iron when needed


Shipping & Delivery 

* Standard Uk delivery (4-5 working days)

* Delivery fees 3.99
